ed, and I was trying to chase.\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I turned fourth, and climbed up one spot, and almost pulled off the overtake at the last gate.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the overtake\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"the last gate\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's kayak cross, and you can have a plan, but nothing goes to plan.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1125, \"end\": 1130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\", \"score\": 0.9999995836015799, \"rank\": 4.163984914566578e-07, \"text\": \"kayak\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a plan\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1174}, {\"ngram\": \"plan\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Noemie Fox leads the field during a kayak cross heat.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1190, \"end\": 1200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noemie Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\"}, {\"begin\": 1226, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\", \"score\": 0.9999995836015799, \"rank\": 4.163984914566578e-07, \"text\": \"kayak\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Noemie is still in with a shot of a medal.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_ph